sg":"個地勢其實唔係好適合做任何抗爭， <br />\n要即散嘅難散， 又冇咩遮頭，又曬又落雨維持唔到好耐，又難提供補給，<br />\n所以未必係個好地點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"但真係對準政權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"但其實咁做對佢冇影響，<br />\n衰啲講句， 面佢就預咗唔要， <span style=\"color: red;\">短期</span>圍禮賓對佢簡直無關痛癢，大不了咪唔返去；<span style=\"color: red;\">長期</span>就更加唔洗諗，引用返頭先講嘅原因"},{"pid":"539192572141fd4a5b1e4c379b6f43016d8e1041","tid":1276444,"uid":260139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"打佢地既弱點<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">資產！</span></span><br />\n股票同樓價我相信好難會做到好大影響<br />\n但係我留意到仲有一樣資產<br />\n我相信係屬於好多保皇黨同埋撐黑警既廢老<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">的士牌</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%258F%25A0&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=1281b7ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0</a><br />\n我地要做既好簡單 就係由呢一刻開始唔再搭的士！<br />\n完全合法！和理非既你地都可以參與<br />\n其實只係改變少少生活習慣選擇其他交通工具<br />\n但有兩個重點<br />\n一定要夠多人參與！<br />\n長時間去做！<br />\n唔好睇小呢個行動，你試諗下，如果全香港突然有100萬人都唔再坐的士，持續1年，會有咩結果呢？<br />\n全港而家有15000部紅的 每個牌值5200000<br />\n加埋係7百幾億（未計綠藍的）<br />\n如果呢個行動堅持落去 只要個牌跌一半<br />\n佢地已經冇左300幾億<br />\n<br />\n明明的士係民生既野，點解會比你班出賣香港既人炒炒賣賣？就好似樓一樣。點解的士可以起標話加價就加價？唔好以為加左落班司機到，因為租金一樣會加！點解uber一直都係唔合法？你們懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係知道佢地一直默默保護緊既野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係佢地既弱點</span></span><br />\n如果你地都想為香港出一分力<br />\n就一齊去做啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果少人去做，係唔會成功<br />\n但我深信我地個心都係有一個信念一個希望！！<br />\n團結就是力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保皇狗，廢老們，的士狗係時候找數喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎一同響應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b7a965273b484951f168d455eb44989bbc6812","tid":1276444,"uid":54965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5df73619d0955eb5047f2f39f5da8396e5891b31","tid":1276444,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac143c79770434e024ac1561fb7eac9b1f55c76","tid":1276444,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649896b154b234a8b7bcc0699b75801a7e1840ed","tid":1276444,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cfc558491c3f1d29878da434988cbe14dfcc99c","tid":1276444,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"個地勢其實唔係好適合做任何抗爭， <br />\n要即散嘅難散， 又冇咩遮頭，又曬又落雨維持唔到好耐，又難提供補給，<br />\n所以未必係個好地點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"但真係對準政權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"但其實咁做對佢冇影響，<br />\n衰啲講句， 面佢就預咗唔要， <span style=\"color: red;\">短期</span>圍禮賓對佢簡直無關痛癢，大不了咪唔返去；<span style=\"color: red;\">長期</span>就更加唔洗諗，引用返頭先講嘅原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"交俾大家討論<br />\n不過我覺得俾人觀感要係搵負責人黎對話既意思<br />\n對準政權"},{"pid":"1379d8ea33080ab61054b0b4e9ff090dac8add0c","tid":1276444,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d58ceb3de49170ee077cdc580736a212052e31","tid":1276444,"uid":271577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"始終無一個精神領袖帶頭，好難成大事，Hunger game就係一例，雖然係電影，但說明左自發性行動只係短暫唔持久，遇到有組織既政府用拖字闕就會變成散沙。<br />\n<br />\n利申：P牌新會然，9up不用理會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"每個人都可以係精神領袖，<br />\n每個人呢一刻都開始要有獨立思考能力， 要識fact check, 要知道後果，要睇住局勢；<br />\n有領袖嘅話，件事未必可以發酵到更大，政府一定會對準嗰個人落手"},{"pid":"2a91c668a6f3ec772e7e015dd87ca941837fe539","tid":1276444,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"539192572141fd4a5b1e4c379b6f43016d8e1041","tid":1276444,"uid":260139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"打佢地既弱點<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">資產！</span></span><br />\n股票同樓價我相信好難會做到好大影響<br />\n但係我留意到仲有一樣資產<br />\n我相信係屬於好多保皇黨同埋撐黑警既廢老<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">的士牌</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%258F%25A0&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=1281b7ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0</a><br />\n我地要做既好簡單 就係由呢一刻開始唔再搭的士！<br />\n完全合法！和理非既你地都可以參與<br />\n其實只係改變少少生活習慣選擇其他交通工具<br />\n但有兩個重點<br />\n一定要夠多人參與！<br />\n長時間去做！<br />\n唔好睇小呢個行動，你試諗下，如果全香港突然有100萬人都唔再坐的士，持續1年，會有咩結果呢？<br />\n全港而家有15000部紅的 每個牌值5200000<br />\n加埋係7百幾億（未計綠藍的）<br />\n如果呢個行動堅持落去 只要個牌跌一半<br />\n佢地已經冇左300幾億<br />\n<br />\n明明的士係民生既野，點解會比你班出賣香港既人炒炒賣賣？就好似樓一樣。點解的士可以起標話加價就加價？唔好以為加左落班司機到，因為租金一樣會加！點解uber一直都係唔合法？你們懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係知道佢地一直默默保護緊既野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係佢地既弱點</span></span><br />\n如果你地都想為香港出一分力<br />\n就一齊去做啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果少人去做，係唔會成功<br />\n但我深信我地個心都係有一個信念一個希望！！<br />\n團結就是力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保皇狗，廢老們，的士狗係時候找數喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎一同響應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"唔計金鐘手足(大部分後生仔女)， 單計普通遊行人士入面有幾多個係的士常客？我覺得有心嘅人可以做， 但的士影響力未必夠大， 但可以試下其他更有影響力交通工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311f908867100ba73679679993694cd1b5de7ddf","tid":1276444,"uid":264459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:28.000Z","msg":"求討論致勝一擊 後續行動<br />\n<br />\n我地一直圍政總警總佔路等等都係處於主動位<br />\n政府就可以完全被動 唔回應9回應都吹佢唔漲<br />\n唔知勇武仲可以升級到咩程度<br />\n好多人今個月以來次次出黎好攰 唔知可以撐到幾時<br />\n所以需要大家一齊brainstorm關鍵一擊<br />\n逼使致府落入主動位置同道德低地<br />\n實行以弱制強<br />\n<br />\n大家唔需要同意我提議既做法 純粹例子<br />\n只想拋磚引玉<br />\n隨便負皮 只求開放討論<br />\n<br />\n[緊急策略] 我地一直處於主動 任政府抹黑冷處理 係時候拋返舊屎比林鄭食了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c142d991b328941636bb5d3632d1f78d62e487e","tid":1276444,"uid":216907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>【 突發】《香港己亥宣言》中英日三語登場！盡力為香港定下重光藍圖！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276561\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276561</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Wc5Mre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Wc5Mre.png&h=41e8b817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vhhUEMm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvhhUEMm.png&h=5569bb48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8be61dd956698dd5f68f75622553e2baff006349","tid":1276444,"uid":216907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87ee778fcefc02b5a196bcb69dc8d664d892d8e6","tid":1276444,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:59:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>【 突發】《香港己亥宣言》中英日三語登場！盡力為香港定下重光藍圖！</strong></span><